{"lemma":"حَدِيقَة","slug":"حَدِيقَة","root":"ح.د.ق","root_slug":"ح-د-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-د-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7375"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"garden (decorative piece of land outside)","examples":[{"text":"فِي الْحَدِيقَةِ يُوجَدُ الْكَثِيرُ مِنَ الْزُّهُورِ وَالْنَّبَاتَاتِ الْجَمِيلَةِ.","english":"In the garden, there are many beautiful flowers and plants."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"park"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Related to حدق (“surround, enclose”)"},"ipa":["/ħa.diː.qa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7375","headword_ar":"حَدِيقَةٌ","root":"Hdq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A walled garden; a garden surrounded by a wall:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, TA:) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylapN","text_ar":"فَعِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlapN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any round piece of land surrounded by a fence"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by elevated land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whatever is surrounded by building:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and, by extension of its application,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a garden, though without a wall:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a meadow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoDap","text_ar":"رَوْضَة"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a garden of palm-trees and of other trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, IDrd, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dense and luxuriant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, IDrd, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fruit-bearing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a garden"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~ap","text_ar":"جَنَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of palmtrees and grape-vines:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a distinct collection of palm-trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a plot of seedproduce:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hollow in a valley, that retains water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any depressed place in a valley, that retains water, thought water be not in its bottom:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadaAy^iqu","text_ar":"حَدَايِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K.) Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa rada EalaY~a kitaAbuka fatanaz~ahotu fiY","text_ar":"وَ رَدَ عَلَىَّ كِتَابُكَ فَتَنَزَّهْتُ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bahojapi HadaAy^iqihi","text_ar":"بَهْجَةِ حَدَايِقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thy letter has come to me, and I have recreated myself in contemplating the beauty of its garden-like phrases"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","TA","K","Zj","IDrd","Kr"]}]}}